languages.text: {n}Спустя час дознаватель выходит из дворца и направляется к вам. Его взгляд мрачен, а скулы напряжены.{/n} "Благодарю. Я готов идти".

traits.locale_text: {n}Спустя час дознаватель выходит из дворца и направляется к вам. Его взгляд мрачен, а скулы напряжены.{/n} "Благодарю за предоставлоенное мне время. Я готов идти".
traits.speaker: HeinrixCompanion

languages.text: {n}An hour later, the Interrogator exits the palace and walks toward you. His eyes are grim, his jaw tense.{/n} "Thank you. I am ready to go."

languages.text: {n}一个小时之后，海因里希走出了大殿，朝你走来。他目光冷峻，下巴紧绷。{/n}“谢谢你，我可以离开了。”
languages.original_text: {n}An hour later, the Interrogator exits the palace and walks toward you. His eyes are grim, his jaw tense.{/n} "Thank you. I am ready to go."

traits.speaker: HeinrixCompanion

languages.text: {n}Una hora más tarde, el interrogador sale del palacio y se acerca a ti. Su mirada es sombría y tiene tensa la mandíbula.{/n} «Gracias. Ya podemos irnos».
languages.original_text: {n}An hour later, the Interrogator exits the palace and walks toward you. His eyes are grim, his jaw tense.{/n} "Thank you. I am ready to go."

languages.text: {n}1時間後、インテロゲイターが宮殿を出てあなたに向かって歩いてくる。その目は険しく、顔はこわばっていた。{/n}「ありがとう。もういい」
languages.original_text: {n}An hour later, the Interrogator exits the palace and walks toward you. His eyes are grim, his jaw tense.{/n} "Thank you. I am ready to go."

languages.text: {n}Une heure plus tard, l'interrogateur émerge du palais. Il s'approche de vous, le regard sinistre et la mâchoire serrée.{/n} « Merci. Nous pouvons y aller. »
languages.original_text: {n}An hour later, the Interrogator exits the palace and walks toward you. His eyes are grim, his jaw tense.{/n} "Thank you. I am ready to go."

languages.text: {n}Eine Stunde später verlässt der Interrogator den Palast und geht auf dich zu. Sein Blick ist finster, sein Kiefer angespannt.{/n} "Danke. Ich bin bereit zu gehen."
languages.original_text: {n}An hour later, the Interrogator exits the palace and walks toward you. His eyes are grim, his jaw tense.{/n} "Thank you. I am ready to go."

languages.text: {n}Sorgucu, bir saat sonra saraydan çıkarak sana doğru yürüyor. Gözlerinde sert bir bakış var. Çenesinde gerginlik seziliyor.{/n} "Teşekkür ederim. Gitmeye hazırım."
